    <div class="pb-5">
        Lutendi Systems Inc. (“Lutendi”, “us”, “we”, “our”) owns and operates the website located at www.lutendi.com (“Website”) and the Lutendi rent reporting platform (“Platform” and together with Website, “Services”). This privacy policy (“Privacy Policy”) describes how we collect, use, and disclose information, including personally identifiable information about an individual (“Personal Information”), which we collect or receive via the Services. Please read the following carefully to understand our practices regarding Personal Information of Users who access and browse the Website or use the Platform.
    </div>
    <div class="pb-5">
        We may change this Privacy Policy from time to time at our sole discretion. Lutendi may require you to provide consent to the updated Privacy Policy before further use of the Services is permitted. 
    </div>
    <div class="pb-5">
        <span class="font-bold">1. Who does this Privacy Policy apply to? </span>With respect to Platform Users, this Privacy policy applies to partners with whom we have executed a separate master subscription agreement (each, a “Partner”) and to individuals who have entered into a rental agreement with a Partner (each, a Resident” and collectively with Partner, “User”, “you”, “your”). We may receive Personal Information about Residents directly from Partners and this Privacy Policy will apply to such Personal Information. This Privacy Policy does not apply to the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information by Partners. Partners may be subject to differing requirements that govern how they collect, use, and disclose a Resident’s Personal Information. We encourage Residents to read the Partner’s respective privacy policy or to contact the Partner directly to understand how Personal Information may be collected, used, and disclosed by that Partner.
    </div>
    <div class="pb-5">
        <span class="font-bold">2. Consent. </span>By using the Services, you consent to the collection, use and disclosure of your Personal Information as described in this Privacy Policy. Except as set forth in this Privacy Policy, your Personal Information will not be collected, used, or disclosed for any other purpose without your consent.
        <br>
        <span class="font-bold">Note: </span>Residents who register for the Platform consent to the sharing of their Personal Information by Partner or Lutendi (as applicable) with Credit Reporting Agencies.
    </div>    
    <div class="pb-5"> 
        <span class="font-bold">3. Personal Information you provide us. </span> You may disclose Personal Information to us as follows:  
        <div class="pl-10">
            <span class="font-bold">a. By creating a Platform account. </span>When Residents register for a Platform account, we collect the following: name, email address, phone number, date of birth, residential address, a copy of the residential lease between Resident and Partner, a copy of government ID, a copy of non-government ID, and any other Personal Information requested by Lutendi during account creation.
            <br>
            <span class="font-bold">b. By using the Services. </span>When you use the Platform or Website, we collect any Personal Information that you provide to us via the Platform. For clarity, we collect any Resident Personal Information shared with us directly by Partners or indirectly by Partners via a Third-Party Integration, such as Resident’s rent payment history, unpaid debts, and relationship with a Partner (including but not limited to a Partner’s account of interactions with a Resident and history of Resident’s conduct).
            <br>
            <span class="font-bold">c. By using Third-Party Integrations. </span>We may integrate with or rely on third-party platforms and services to provide the Services to you (“Third-Party Integrations”). Any Personal Information submitted to us via Third-Party Integrations that we can access will be subject to this Privacy Policy, but please note that such Personal Information will also be subject to the terms of the applicable Third-Party Integration.
            <br>
            <span class="font-bold">d. By contacting us. </span>When you contact us (whether via email, the Services, or a Third-Party Integration), we collect any Personal Information you choose to provide to us. Any Personal Information shared via a Third-Party Integration will be subject to this Privacy Policy, but please note that your Personal Information will also be subject to the terms of the applicable Third-Party Integration.
            <br>
            <span class="font-bold">e. By applying to work with us. </span>If you would like to work with us and submit hiring materials to us, we collect any Personal Information you share with us in your hiring materials, such as your resume, cover letter, transcripts, or certifications. If you are a current Lutendi employee and would like more information about how we collect, use, and disclose your Personal Information, please contact us per Section 11 below.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pb-5">
        <span class="font-bold">4. Personal Information we collect when you use the Services. </span>When you use the Services, Lutendi may collect certain information through technologies such as cookies and other automatic data collection technologies (“Cookies”). We may use Cookies for authentication and to compile aggregate statistics about usage of the Services, such as how long Users spend using the Platform, and what parts or pages of the Website are viewed most often. This information is used to improve the content and operation of the Services. We may also use Cookies to promote the Services through marketing and advertising. These Cookies may be accessed or disclosed to third parties for the purpose of serving you relevant advertisements. You may opt out of Cookies or prevent third-party websites from accessing our Cookies by adjusting your privacy settings on your browser. However, opting out of Cookies may disable some features of the Services and may prevent us from providing you with the information and services you have requested.
