            <br>
            <span class="font-bold">h. </span>For other purposes for which we provide notice at the time the Personal Information is collected.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pb-5">
        <span class="font-bold">6. Who We Share Your Information With. </span>We may share your Personal Information with our employees and with third parties, such as our affiliates, selected business partners, suppliers, and sub-contractors, while performing our contractual obligations. These third parties include credit reporting agencies with whom we have a contractual relationship (each a “Credit Reporting Agency”). These third parties may also include web hosting partners, IT service providers, and advertisers.
        <br><br>
